  "correctAnswer": "Generate a detailed competitor analysis report for a fintech startup. The report should analyze exactly 3 to 5 major competitors in the fintech space and cover the following areas for each competitor — what their core product or service is and who their target customers are, what their biggest strengths are and what they do better than anyone else in the market, what their weaknesses or gaps are that the fintech startup could potentially take advantage of, what their pricing model looks like and how it compares to the market, and what their online presence and customer reputation looks like based on reviews and public perception. After analyzing all competitors, end the report with a summary section that highlights the 3 biggest opportunities the fintech startup can act on based on the gaps and weaknesses found across all competitors. Present the report in a clear and structured format with a separate section for each competitor so it is easy to read and compare.",
